| .cursor/rules/ (Forge + Versonas) | OK / Partial / Missing | … |
| Tasklets / Sampling (optional) | Installed / Not installed | … |
| Alignment check | Run / N/A | … |

### Next commands (ordered)

1. …
2. …

### Optional next steps

- Tasklets + Sampling: `bash blueprints/sdlc/methodologies/forge/tasklets/install-tasklets.sh`
- Skills: copy from `blueprints/sdlc/templates/forge/cursor-skills/`

### Handoff

- If team config incomplete: use **@forge-setup** or `blueprints/sdlc/methodologies/forge/setup/QUESTIONNAIRE.md`
